    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership price tag? This car is an absolute dream and has been my pride and joy. It\u2019s in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this beauty since day one, keeping it polished and perfectly maintained. You won't find a single scratch or dent anywhere. Come take it for a spin; I promise you're going to fall in love!",
