    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true showroom masterpiece, meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster without a single rock chip or swirl mark, further protected by a high-end ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, the original floor mats are pristine, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service history that confirms its pampered life. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this car offers a rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive excellence that looks and drives exactly as it did on the delivery floor.",
